h4. Problem:
When creating an LDAP directory type connector with _LDAP Permissions_ set to _Read Only, with Local Groups_, you can't include members into groups that are pulled from the LDAP.
h4. Steps to reproduce:
# Create a connector directory and set it to read-only with local groups;
